  "texts": [
    "This component serves as the control center for the discussion process, orchestrating a structured deliberation flow as shown in Figure4.",
    "It unfolds as follows: [Thought Elicitation] Participants express their WoE on each dimension; AI responds with its perspectives.",
    "[Discussion] AI highlights commonalities and discrepancies, inviting participants to provide justifications or question differing viewpoints.",
    "AI responds with critical insights.",
    "All three components of the Communication layer (Intention Analyzer, Deliberation Facilitator, and Argument Evaluator) play vital roles in this phase."
  ]
}